Sense includes a compiled form of the Rime “pinyin-simp” dictionary.

Source: https://github.com/rime/rime-pinyin-simp
Dictionary: pinyin_simp.dict.yaml
Authors: Gong Chen and Android Open Source Project contributors
License: Apache License 2.0
License copy: licenses/rime-pinyin-simp-LICENSE

The binary file at ime-service/src/main/assets/pinyin_lexicon.bin is generated
by tools/build_pinyin_lexicon.py. The upstream dictionary is not modified except
for whitespace normalization, duplicate removal, ranking, and binary encoding.
